Invocation Name: my medicine cabinet part two
des:
My Medicine Cabinet skill is an app designed by the pharmacist informatics team from Belmont University College of Pharmacy. The app can provide you with the answers to many of your questions about most of the medication you are taking, as well as the other important information you need to know about this medication. 

This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment, or diagnosis. The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
